room_title: Escape room "Adam's County Insane Asylum" by Behind Locked Doors in Quincy
room_description: Welcome to Adam's County Insane Asylum, where we aim to eliminate you... I mean your mental illnesses, of course! Please drop your belongings off at the admission's counter, you won't be needing them ever again, and follow me. Here at ACIA, those that are admitted never leave... without their sanity back, obviously. But some people just can't be helped. You can't escape crazy... or can you?
